Package: PortfolioTesteR
Type: Package
Title: Test Investment Strategies with English-Like Code
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alberto", "Pallotta",
           email = "pallottaalberto@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to design, backtest, and analyze portfolio strategies using
    simple, English-like function chains. Includes technical indicators such as
    momentum via calc_momentum(), Relative Strength Index via calc_rsi(), and
    moving averages; flexible stock selection (e.g., filter_top_n(), 
    filter_by_percentile()); portfolio construction (e.g., weight_equally(),
    weight_by_signal()); and a compact backtesting engine run_backtest() for
    portfolio returns, drawdowns, and summary metrics. Example workflows run 
    quickly and offline using included sample datasets.
